{
  "stem": "21004.7",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "What do you-- what did you do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "What kind-- you have no medication.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She say I'll tell you what's happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With all my pain and everything, and they were blowing, and I fall asleep.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I was sleeping, my mother came to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother came to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She grabbed me around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she say [GERMAN], you will survive only here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Don't go from here no place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Here you'll survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I woke up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's what happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everything disappeared.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No blisters, no nothing, dry completely.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You don't have to put any medication.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't have to put on no medication at all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So yeah, I say there is miracle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "People used to say there is miracles, but now I see there is something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's the way we survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Only here in the woods, you survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Don't move from here no place, you'll survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then, when I finished the bunker-- when I finished, I went again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I went by myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "No, I took [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Belcher ?] with me always.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I took [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Belcher ?] with me to go to my Polish friend.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Went there and tell him what I need, that he should build for me from metal an oven, a metal oven, to burn with wood and with pipes that the smoke goes out the pipes.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I told him to make like two three footers-- actually, two or three footers-- the pipe should be one go on top of the other.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Now the pipe should go higher than the trees, that the-- it wouldn't smoke up the trees.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Once it would smoke up the trees, somebody would spot it, would say something is funny here.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
